cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to 0 will cause invalid thread configuration, leading to processing failures in the CU.

du.explanation_en: Setting pdsch_AntennaPorts_XP to 5 (invalid value) will cause antenna configuration errors and cell setup failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 pdsch_AntennaPorts_XP 設定為 5（無效值）將導致天線配置錯誤和細胞設置失敗。
